This is a missed-optimization in ConstraintElimination.

The following program reveals the missed optimization.
The source program is
```llvm
define i1 @test_decompose_sub_nsw_sgt_zero_inv(i32 %x, i32 %y) {
entry:
  %sub = sub nsw i32 %y, %x
  %cond = icmp sgt i32 %sub, 10
  br i1 %cond, label %if.then, label %if.else

if.then:                                          ; preds = %entry
  %ret = icmp sge i32 %x, %y
  ret i1 %ret

if.else:                                          ; preds = %entry
  ret i1 true
}

```

However, current LLVM cannot optimize the source program. The expected optimized program is
```llvm
define i1 @test_decompose_sub_nsw_sgt_zero_inv(i32 %x, i32 %y) {
entry:
